
This patch adds capability to run EIT scans in schedulled mode where scans will be in defined time windows.

EIT scanner will switch to schedulled collecting of EIT if EITCrawIdleStart setting is bigger than 3600.
If EITCrawIdleStart value is higher than 3600, EIT scanner will:
 - start EITCrawIdleStart seconds after midnight
 - will scan for EITCrawDuration minutes
If EITCrawDuration setting is is not defined, EIT scan duration will run for default 240min (4h).

Example:
